uk.ac.ox.cs.diadem.oxpath.model

Class OXPathContextNodeConstructed

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ox.cs.diadem.oxpath.model.OXPathContextNode
      • uk.ac.ox.cs.diadem.oxpath.model.OXPathContextNodeConstructed
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<OXPathContextNode>

    public class OXPathContextNodeConstructed
extends OXPathContextNode
    Wrapper for DOM nodes that do not come from the browser. Currently, this includes notional root and the style nodes, as they have no analogue in DOM. Provides a minimal construction of a DOM Node so compareTo works correctly for the sorted node list
    Author:
    AndrewJSel, Giovanni Grasso
